## STEP 2 — Stripe Webhooks

Go to https://dashboard.stripe.com/webhooks → Add endpoint

- URL: https://YOUR-NETLIFY-SITE.netlify.app/.netlify/functions/stripe-webhook
- Events to enable:
  - customer.subscription.created
  - customer.subscription.updated
  - customer.subscription.deleted
  - invoice.payment_succeeded
  - invoice.payment_failed

After saving, copy the Signing Secret (whsec_...) and add it to Netlify
env vars as STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET.

Also create your products in Stripe → Products → Add product (Pro, Team, Enterprise).
Copy the price_XXXX IDs and paste them into the INSERT above.

---

## STEP 3 — Netlify Environment Variables

Netlify Dashboard → Site settings → Environment variables → Add all of these:

### Required (nothing works without these)
| Variable              | Value                                              |
|-----------------------|----------------------------------------------------|
| DATABASE_URL          | Neon connection string (postgres://...)            |
| JWT_SECRET            | Random 64-char string (use: openssl rand -hex 32)  |
| KAIXU_GATE_TOKEN      | Bearer token for kAIxU gateway                     |

### Required for email
| Variable              | Value                                              |
|-----------------------|----------------------------------------------------|
| SENDGRID_API_KEY      | From SendGrid dashboard                            |
| SMTP_FROM_EMAIL       | e.g. hello@kaixu.app                              |
| APP_URL               | Your Netlify site URL (https://kaixu.netlify.app)  |

### Required for billing
| Variable              | Value                                              |
|-----------------------|----------------------------------------------------|
| STRIPE_SECRET_KEY     | sk_live_... or sk_test_... from Stripe             |
| STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET | whsec_... from Stripe webhook (see Step 2)         |

### Optional
| Variable              | Value                                              |
|-----------------------|----------------------------------------------------|
| KAIXU_GATE_BASE       | https://kaixu67.skyesoverlondon.workers.dev        |
| KAIXU_DEFAULT_MODEL   | kAIxU-flash (this is already the default)          |
| DATABASE_REPLICA_URL  | Neon read replica URL (falls back to primary)      |
| GITHUB_CLIENT_ID      | GitHub OAuth App client ID                         |
| GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET  | GitHub OAuth App client secret                     |
| SENTRY_DSN            | From Sentry dashboard (error tracking)             |
| SAML_CERT             | SAML IdP certificate (for SAML SSO)                |
| SAML_PRIVATE_KEY      | SAML SP private key (for SAML SSO)                 |

