## STEP 4 — Pre-flight Validation

After setting all env vars, run locally before going live:

```bash
npm run setup:check        # checks env vars + model name compliance
npm run setup:check:all    # + live DB connection, gateway ping, Stripe format
```

All items should show PASS. Fix anything that shows FAIL before deploying.

---

## STEP 5 — Health Check

After deploying to Netlify:

```
GET https://YOUR-SITE.netlify.app/.netlify/functions/health
```

Expected response:
```json
{ "ok": true, "db": "ok", "gate": "ok" }
```

If db or gate shows "error", check DATABASE_URL and KAIXU_GATE_TOKEN.

