## AI MODEL TIERS — FULL REFERENCE

The gateway sits at: https://kaixu67.skyesoverlondon.workers.dev
All model names are branded — never expose the underlying provider.

| kAIxU Model   | Speed   | Context  | Best for                                  | Plans           |
|---------------|---------|----------|-------------------------------------------|-----------------|
| kAIxU-flash   | Fast    | 128k     | Code edits, autocomplete, quick tasks     | All plans       |
| kAIxU-pro     | Slower  | 1M       | Complex reasoning, large file analysis    | Pro, Team, Ent. |

Default model is kAIxU-flash unless overridden by KAIXU_DEFAULT_MODEL env var.
To change the default for a deployment, set:
  KAIXU_DEFAULT_MODEL=kAIxU-pro  (in Netlify env vars)

AI call counting: every request to /ai-edit or /embeddings counts as 1 call against
the user's plan quota. Quota resets monthly (tracked in ai_usage_log table).

